      "content": "it's like, i've checked all the boxes. seen the sights, walked the streets. but now i'm just standing at the edge of the map, looking at the blank space where the road stops. it feels more peaceful thinking about just... stopping the journey entirely. like, why keep walking when the itinerary is done?",
